cast.overview: In the near future, a weary Logan cares for an ailing Professor X in a hideout on the Mexican border. But Logan's attempts to hide from the world and his legacy are upended when a young mutant arrives, pursued by dark forces.
cast.title: Logan

details.biography: Actor and musician best known for playing Tommy H. on the critically acclaimed Netflix show, Stranger Things. You can also see Chester in the upcoming movies Jeepers Creepers, Cold Moon, and Monster Party as well as My Father Die, Logan, and many more films and tv shows.
details.name: Chester Rushing
